<% content_for :title, "Our Process | Jack SaaS" %>

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Our Process</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600">A proven, transparent approach to delivering custom software solutions. We keep you involved every step of the way.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="space-y-20 md:space-y-32">
      <%# Step 1: Discovery %>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium mb-4">Step 1</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Discovery</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">We start by understanding your business, workflows, and pain points. Through workshops and interviews, we identify automation opportunities.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500"><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Duration:</span> 1-2 weeks</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500"><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Deliverables:</span> Discovery Report, Technical Requirements, Project Scope</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-2xl bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl">🔍</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# Step 2: Proposal %>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-2xl bg-cyan-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl">📝</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 text-sm font-medium mb-4">Step 2</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Proposal</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Based on our findings, we create a detailed proposal with scope, timeline, and pricing. You'll know exactly what to expect before we start.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500"><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Duration:</span> 1 week</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500"><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Deliverables:</span> Detailed Proposal, Architecture Document, Project Agreement</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# Step 3: Development %>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 text-sm font-medium mb-4">Step 3</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Development</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Our team develops your solution using agile methodology. Regular check-ins keep you informed, and iterations ensure we get it right.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500"><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Duration:</span> 4-12 weeks</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500"><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Deliverables:</span> Working Software, Documentation, Test Reports</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-2xl bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl">💻</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# Step 4: Launch %>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-2xl bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl">🚀</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-sm font-medium mb-4">Step 4</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Launch</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">We deploy your solution and provide training. Our support continues post-launch to ensure smooth adoption and ongoing success.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500"><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Duration:</span> 2 weeks</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500"><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Deliverables:</span> Live Application, Training, 30-Day Support Plan</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-blue-600">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Start Your Project?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-blue-100 mb-8">Let's begin with a free discovery session. We'll explore your challenges and outline a path forward.</p>
      <a href="/quote" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">
        Start Discovery Phase
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
